<title>SWEDEN: Sandvik says redemption price 197.16 a share.</title>
<headline>Sandvik says redemption price 197.16 a share.</headline>
<dateline>STOCKHOLM 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Swedish tools and speciality metals group Sandvik AB said on Friday it set the price for its four billion crown redemption at 197.16 crowns a share.  </p>
<p>The price was set by calculating the average market price during the last three days of the offering period minus three percent, the company said in a statement.</p>
<p>The offering period ran from May 7 to May 22.</p>
<p>Sandvik will redeem 20,288,090 shares, reducing the total number of shares to 258,188,290, the company said.</p>
<p>Payment is due the last week of June, Sandvik said.</p>
<p>-- Birgitta Forsberg, Stockholm newsroom +46-8-700 1017</p>
